    "answer_id" : 7130374,
    "question_id" : 7123580,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>This is why Guava has an <a href=\"http://docs.guava-libraries.googlecode.com/git/javadoc/com/google/common/primitives/Ints.html#toArray%28java.util.Collection%29\"><code>Ints.toArray(Collection&lt;Integer&gt;)</code></a> method, returning <code>int[]</code>.</p>\n"
  }, {
