      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "You can do this for a shorter version: <code>set.stream().mapToInt(i -&gt; i).toArray()</code>. Auto-unboxing will handle the conversion from <code>Integer</code> so you don&#39;t need <code>Integer::intValue</code>."
