    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>With java 8: </p>\n\n<pre><code>Set&lt;Integer&gt; set = new HashSet&lt;&gt;(); \n// TODO: Add implement for set\n\nint[] array = set.stream().mapToInt(Integer::intValue).toArray();\n</code></pre>\n"
