    "last_activity_date" : 1761528538,
    "last_edit_date" : 1761528538,
    "creation_date" : 1761514966,
    "answer_id" : 79800329,
    "question_id" : 7123580,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>A more modern solution may be to use the stream API as follows:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>// Initialize a hash set.\nSet&lt;Integer&gt; s = new HashSet&lt;&gt;();\ns.add(10);\ns.add(20);\ns.add(30);\n\nint[] arr = s.stream() // Convert the HashSet to a stream.\n            .mapToInt(Integer::intValue) // Map all values to an integer.\n            .toArray(); // Convert the stream to an array.\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
